# Separator — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/separator.css`

## CSS Classes

- `.acko-separator` — base
- `.acko-separator-horizontal` — `@apply w-full`, `height: 1px`, `background: var(--color-control-border-selector)`
- `.acko-separator-vertical` — `height: 100%`, `width: 1px`, `background: var(--color-control-border-selector)`
- `.acko-separator-with-label` — `@apply flex items-center gap-3`
- `.acko-separator-line` — `@apply flex-1`, same background as base
- `.acko-separator-label-text` — `font-size: var(--font-caption-size); color: var(--color-text-muted); white-space: nowrap`

## Accessibility

- When `decorative: true` — `role="none"`
- When `decorative: false` — `role="separator"` with `aria-orientation`
